WEBVTT

00:00.767 --> 00:03.129
ï»¿South Korea's route to the World Cup finals in Brazil...

00:03.255 --> 00:05.178
...was less straightforward than they would have liked.

00:05.650 --> 00:09.299
An uninspiring campaign saw Choi Kang-Hee step down as coach.

00:09.780 --> 00:13.753
They eventually grabbed the final automatic qualifying spot from Asia on goal difference...

00:13.819 --> 00:16.404
...after a defeat to Iran in their final home match.

00:17.058 --> 00:19.966
Hong Myung-Bo, one of the heroes of the 2002 side...

00:20.061 --> 00:22.646
...that went all the way to the semifinals on home soil,...

00:23.012 --> 00:25.594
...is now installed as the man who will lead them to Brazil.

